+Spoilers

-no!


The trees are only capable of using voice clips to communicate! If you notice, during the anomalous calls, (where Leigh isn't the one that's talking), the only words present are ones that have been used in previous conversations!

Ideally, I can get some voice actresses to voice the parts in some actual audio logs, do some fancy effects and seal this SCP up!




